.TH DELPHI-GLYPH 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
glyph \- Look up Unicode characters by codepoint, name, range, or search term
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBglyph\fR [\fB\-\-range\fR] [\fB\-\-search\fR] [\fB\-\-limit\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIINPUT\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Look up Unicode characters by codepoint, name, range, or search term
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-range\fR \fI<RANGE>\fR
Named Unicode block/range (e.g. arrows, latin, greek)
.TP
\fB\-\-search\fR \fI<SEARCH>\fR
Search Unicode names matching this query
.TP
\fB\-\-limit\fR \fI<LIMIT>\fR [default: 50]
Limit number of search results
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIINPUT\fR]
A codepoint (U+0041 or 0x41) or a single character
